original: intros n m. split. - rewrite Nat.max_comm. rewrite Nat.max_comm with (n := n). apply Nat.le_trans with (m := n). apply Nat.le_max_r. - rewrite Nat.max_comm. rewrite Nat.max_comm with (m := S m). apply Nat.le_trans with (m := S m). apply Nat.le_max_l.
